name: Simone's Arrival
description: "From the planet Xaerthiya, Simone arrives." I use GANs to generate portraits and bring them life in new ways through stories, reflections, and if they are lucky, 3D skins for their own autonomy in the digital world. This is my first AI child, Simone. She/they is a calm, introspective creature with a strong force within. [/[made with GANs, Daz, and TouchDesigner]\]
